    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>In the depths of a forest none dare set foot in, a young man awakens with no memory of his past…</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Transcendence Legacy - Voidswept is a fantasy 2D turn-based RPG set in a world ruined by a great catastrophe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/015f0a09ab19a5a6babbf568f977858b.poster.avif?t=1768953084\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/015f0a09ab19a5a6babbf568f977858b.webm?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/015f0a09ab19a5a6babbf568f977858b.mp4?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One year prior, a dark cloud of emptiness shrouded the land and gave birth to unknown, malicious creatures. Faced with an unforeseen calamity, the civilization of humanity collapsed in an instant. Then, strange ruins began to appear throughout the land.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Uncover the truth behind a world plagued by monstrosities. Traverse mysterious ruins in search of answers, with dependable allies by your side.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Classic Turn-Based Combat</strong> <br>Plan each move carefully in a tactical battle system inspired by genre classics</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/8d731ca165907b8dfb0937904b51355d.poster.avif?t=1768953084\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/8d731ca165907b8dfb0937904b51355d.webm?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/8d731ca165907b8dfb0937904b51355d.mp4?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Party-Based Skill Synergy</strong><br>Master over 40 abilities and customize your party’s loadout for every encounter. Skills grow stronger and more efficient as you use them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/d8da1d896fdac620909f7575a81edf09.poster.avif?t=1768953084\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/d8da1d896fdac620909f7575a81edf09.webm?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/d8da1d896fdac620909f7575a81edf09.mp4?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore a Ravaged World</strong><br>Discover hidden items, secret passages, and optional bosses throughout mysterious ruins.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Progression Through Strategy</strong><br>Equip new gear, level up skills, and unlock powerful character enhancements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-Rich Journey</strong><br>Follow an emotionally driven story with optional paths and meaningful character interactions.  Deepen bonds with your allies to unlock unique abilities and learn their backstories.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/6768026a427cb82c0f1b9e98aecc85c7.poster.avif?t=1768953084\" width=780 height=316 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/6768026a427cb82c0f1b9e98aecc85c7.webm?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1814570/extras/6768026a427cb82c0f1b9e98aecc85c7.mp4?t=1768953084\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
